items.title: Awesome Go
items.content_text:
### DevOps Tools / Libraries for creating HTTP middlewares

*   [Mantil (⭐112)](https://github.com/mantil-io/mantil) - Go specific framework for building serverless applications on AWS that enables you to focus on pure Go code while Mantil takes care of the infrastructure.
items.content_html:

items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Themes / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [voidy (⭐0)](https://github.com/rwejdling/voidy) - Borrows elements from [lambda (⭐180k)](https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/blob/master/themes/lambda.zsh-theme) and [robbyrussell (⭐180k)](https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/blob/master/themes/robbyrussell.zsh-theme) themes and adds the active [aws-vault (⭐8.8k)](https://github.com/99designs/aws-vault) profile to the right side of the prompt.
items.content_html:
Themes / superconsole - Windows-only

  • voidy (⭐0) - Borrows elements from lambda (⭐180k) and robbyrussell (⭐180k) themes and adds the active aws-vault (⭐8.8k) profile to the right side of the prompt.

items.title: Awesome Agi Cocosci
items.content_text:

*   [Causal Curiosity: RL Agents Discovering Self-supervised Experiments for Causal Representation Learning](https://arxiv.org/abs/2010.03110) - ***ICML'21***, 2021. \[[All Versions](https://scholar.google.com/scholar?cluster=4880520597219138666\&hl=en\&as_sdt=0,5)].
